- [x] Category
  - [x] get Categories
  - [x] new Category (Not work on typecho >= 1.2)
  - [x] delete Category
- [x] Tag
  - [x] get Tags
- [x] Attachment
  - [x] get attachment/attachments
  - [x] new attachment
- [x] Comment
  - [x] get comment/comments
